name: Comparision
query:
select 
	  a.item_code as "Item Name::150",
	  a.actual_qty as "Balance Qty:Float:140",
	  b.qty_after_transaction as "After Transaction:Float:140",
	  max(b.posting_date)
 from `tabBin` a 
 join `tabStock Ledger Entry` b
 ON a.item_code = b.item_code 
          where b.item_code= select b.posting_date from `tabStock Ledger Entry` b Group By b.item_code
